<p>We must update the field data sorting <code>sorting</code>.</p>  <p>I set <code>$TCA['tx_table2']['ctrl']['sortby'] = 'sorting';</code></p>  <p>And i set: </p>  <pre><code>$TCA['tx_table1']['columns']['uid_records'] = array(             ............                     'config' =&gt; array(                 'type' =&gt; 'inline',                 'languageMode' =&gt; 'inherit',                 'foreign_table' =&gt; 'tx_table2',                 'foreign_sortby' =&gt; 'sorting',                 'size' =&gt; 1,                 'minitems' =&gt; 0,                 'maxitems' =&gt; 100,             ) ); </code></pre>  <p>But when moving the recording position, the data field <code>sorting</code> is not updated. Values are recorded only when creating a new record.</p>  <p>What could be the problem?</p>